<br>
Personally, I'd want something more complicated than the typical fantasy fare, as it would allow for less stereotypical RP. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Illudin Arbitrator &lt;Society of Adventurers&gt;<br>
